title: Sirina H Gynaika tou Viomixanou kai oi Kollites tis 2013 DvdRip
description:
Sirina H Gynaika tou Viomixanou kai oi Kollites tis 2013 DvdRip

I anwmali syzygos Ellina megaloviomixanou exei metatrepsei to ergostasio tou andras tis, apo xwro ergasias, se kentro orgiwn opou mazeyontai kavlwmenoi andres apo oli tin Athina prokeimenou na... eksypiretisoun tin idia kai tis filenades tis.
To tromero tis ypothesis einai oti i ksanammeni kyria viomixanou den eksantlei tin anwmalia tis stin idia, alla parasyrei toso tis files kai kollites tis, oso kai ton evypolipto syzygo tis se akolastes prakseis, me kyrio xaraktiristiko na tin pidane mprosta tou!

Stin olokainourgia paragwgi tis Sirina, i opoia gyristike se pragmatikes synthikes varias viomixanias, prwtagwnistoyn kai... mageyoun i ksanammeni Gioyli kai oi kavlwmenes mexri anwmalias Ellinides, Pinelopi, Sani kai Elisavet.
Se rolous... gewtrypanwn kai sklira ergazomenwn ypallilwn oi Zafeiris, Giorgio, Kenzo, Apollwnios, Odysseas kai Maniatis. I synexeia stis othones sas...

PAIZOUN OI: GIOULI, SANI, ELISAVET, PINELOPI, ZAFEIRIS, KENZO, ODYSSEAS
